Package com.mx.babel.employee.db.model

Class EventLog

java.lang.Object
com.mx.babel.employee.db.model.EventLog
@Entity public class EventLog extends Object
Entity class to represent the event_log table. This table stores event logs related to employee actions (CREATE, UPDATE, DELETE).
